testcaseName: Child under 9 received one in previous season and one in current season
generalDescription: This test case describes when a child under 9 years of age received one dose of the Influenza vaccine in a previous season and one in the current season that an additional dose is recommended in the current season. Forecast second dose at 4 weeks later.
